Preferences\/InputOutput\/HDMIOutputMoni.translation: Display camera's live view (with camera info) on an HDTV. Requires Media Mod and HDMI cable (both sold separately).

Preferences\/InputOutput\/HDMIOutputMedi.translation: Play back your media on an HDTV. Requires Media Mod and HDMI cable (both sold separately).

Preferences\/InputOutput\/HDMIOutputLive.translation: Show camera's live view (without camera info) on an HDTV. Requires Media Mod and HDMI cable (both sold separately).
